entry.title: Russia Unleashes Biggest Barrage of Strikes on Ukraine Since Invasion
entry.content: Waves of Russian missiles slammed into Kyiv and other Ukrainian cities in one of the broadest and most intense bombardments of the war, in response to a weekend attack Moscow blamed on Ukraine that seriously damaged a bridge connecting Russia to occupied Crimea.

entry.title: How Police Tactics at Indonesia Soccer Stadium Led to Disaster That Killed 131
entry.content: Fans say thousands were forced to run to exits because police fired tear gas into the stands after a match.
